$ON_PRDFRM
Onevent BEFORE_AREA Gosub AV_PRDFRM From W1GENEMPV
Return

$AV_PRDFRM
Chgfmt [M]PRDFRM(indice) With "DZ:"+GFMDAT
Gosub _AFF
Return

